@node MAIN
@title "The Last Cardassians"
==============================================================================
                           The Last Cardassians
==============================================================================
         A scenario for the game "-Star_Trek-" by Frank Mathieson
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

+++ UNITED FEDERATION OF PLANETS
+++ STARFLEET HEADQUARTERS
+++ STARDATE 50998.5
+++ ADMIRAL VLADIKOV

Dear Captain H.-R. WATERS,

the Cardassians have been defeated, the ships of the Federation and the
Bajorans have finally invaded Cardassia Prime.

The last Cardassian cruisers have been reported to have joined at system
Trivia-9 to a last, giantic battle fleet. We know most of the ships have
been involved in recent battles, so they are damaged and not that strong
as you are used to, but it really are MANY ships.

The USS VECTOR (NCC-1742) has order to immediatly join the Federation
fleet to defend us against the probably last strike of the Cardassians.

Good luck, Captain!
==============================================================================
