@node SCENARIOOVERVIEW
@title "What is in this scenario?"

@{b}OVERVIEW@{ub}

Estimated difficulty: Medium
Solvable with unregistered version: Yes (tested) - but here, the
registered version is HIGHLY recommended!

This is an interesting, not that easy to win scenario, but more
experienced players should be able to do it in around 50 turns.
The enemy ships are weaker than you are used to, but there are lots
of them! Since you have not that much starbases, you will not have
much time to upgrade your ship. Try to defeat the enemy quickly even
with a not so perfect ship before all starbases are destroyed.
